$url = 'https://petscan.wmflabs.org/'
$resp = irm $url -Body @{doit=1; language='ru'; project='wikisource'; categories='Списки редакций'; depth=1; format='json';}
$resp.'*'[0].a.'*' | ? -Not nstext | select -excl metadata,n,nstext -Property @{n='web';e={'https://ru.wikisource.org/w/index.php?curid='+$_.id}},* | Format-HtmlTable -Description (gcb -Raw) -OutVariable htmlFile | Invoke-Item
